	{
		screen_text = "You would be nuts to go to Hiroth. It's not far from here, but the journey is extremely treacherous. You'll want to exit town via the upper stairs to the west. Follow the torches until you meet up with the road in Quillrabe Canyons, then head south until you reach the Drake Nest cave. If you can sneak past the Dragon Queen and her drakes, you should be able to find your way. Keep to the south and east walls when you come to the split. The Nest exits into Hiroth Ravine, which is just outside of Hiroth proper. Follow the river and you will see Lake Hiroth ahead, with the town around its banks. ";
